OL,3,CBoy, 14, riding e-bike dies day after
OL,4,Ccar collision
OL,6,FA teenager who was riding an e-bike
OL,7,Fhas died following a collision with a
OL,8,Fcar in Chesterfield.
OL,10,FFinley Dawson, 14, was riding the e-
OL,11,Fbike in Newbold Road on Thursday 5
OL,12,FMarch when it collided with a car.
OL,14,FFinley and his passenger, a 15-year-
OL,15,Fold boy, were thrown from the e-bike
OL,16,Fafter it hit a Kia Sportage.
OL,18,FBoth teenagers were taken to hospital
OL,19,Fwith serious injuries.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
