PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773169881
OL,3,CBoy, 14, riding e-bike dies day after
OL,4,Ccar collision
OL,6,FFinley died the following day, after
OL,7,Fhis injuries were described by medics
OL,8,Fas 'non-survivable'.
OL,10,FThe 15-year-old boy remains in a
OL,11,Fserious but stable condition.
OL,13,FThe families of both teenager have
OL,14,Fissued a joint statement about the
OL,15,Fdangers of riding e-bikes on the road:
OL,17,F"There is a reason these bikes are
OL,18,Fbanned from the road, and
OL,19,Fdevastatingly Finley has paid the
OL,20,Fultimate price in losing his life.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
