PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773169881
OL,3,CBoy, 14, riding e-bike dies day after
OL,4,Ccar collision
OL,6,F"His friend has sustained serious
OL,7,Finjuries and has to come to terms with
OL,8,Fgrowing up without his best mate.
OL,10,F"Although the thrill of riding an e-
OL,11,Fbike on the road seems exciting, it
OL,12,Fcan also be fatal.
OL,14,F"That quick thrill, is not worth the
OL,15,Frisk."
OL,17,FDerbyshire Police said: "Finley's
OL,18,Ffamily are being supported by
OL,19,Fspecialist officers, and our thoughts
OL,20,Fgo out to them at this difficult time.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUwD@FO]
